*corefonts-1-r1 (03 Feb 2004)

  03 Feb 2004; <augustus@gentoo.org> corefonts-1-r1.ebuild:
  Fixed installion of corefonts to depend on x11 and to install the fonts.scale
  and fonts.dir files. Also added the hints about XF86Config changes. Added
  ~amd64 keyword.

  25 Jan 2004; Sven Blumenstein <bazik@gentoo.org> corefonts-1.ebuild:
  Stable on sparc.

